short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension modifies the outlook of the Difference column in the Compare mode of the performance table in Google Search Console.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension modifies the outlook of the Difference column in the Compare mode of the Position data set in the Performance tab in Google Search Console to make it easier for SEO specialists to read, understand, and analyze the report.
